OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPerhaps some early sunshine
OL,6,Fover the Angus Coast otherwise a
OL,7,Fcloudy day. A few showers then more
OL,8,Fpersistent rain soon reaching the
OL,9,FTrossachs extending northeast to reach
OL,10,Fall areas by afternoon. Turning
OL,11,Fshowery by evening but some heavy
OL,12,Fshowers.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRather cloudy with further
OL,15,Fshowers this evening, some heavy. The
OL,16,Fshowers turning lighter and more
OL,17,Fscattered overnight before more rain
OL,18,Freturns to the Central Belt towards
OL,19,Fmorning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
