OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRather cloudy with rain or
OL,6,Fshowers, some turning heavy at times.
OL,7,FWinds will be mainly light.
OL,8,
OL,9,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBrighter
OL,10,Fwith sunny intervals and a few showers
OL,11,Fon Friday. Rain spreading from west on
OL,12,FSaturday, turning heavy in west. Then
OL,13,Fback to sunshine and showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
